.TH "ice_flow_set_rss_seg_info" 9 "ice_flow_set_rss_seg_info" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
ice_flow_set_rss_seg_info \- setup packet segments for RSS
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "enum ice_status" ice_flow_set_rss_seg_info
.BI "(struct ice_flow_seg_info *segs "  ","
.BI "u64 hash_fields "  ","
.BI "u32 flow_hdr "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "segs" 12
pointer to the flow field segment(s)
.IP "hash_fields" 12
fields to be hashed on for the segment(s)
.IP "flow_hdr" 12
protocol header fields within a packet segment
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Helper function to extract fields from hash bitmap and use flow
header value to set flow field segment for further use in flow
profile entry or removal.
